latestIgtvVideos.title: My Night care routine 😴
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I love maintaining a fit body , healthy skin n a balanced diet

And 
I always believe in taking extra care of my skin in the night than in the day , cuz it’s very impt to rinse ur face thoroughly n moisturiser ur face before goin to bed. 
So , here’s my simple , inexpensive, yet a feel good night care routine 😉

These are the products I use before going to bed. • Baby oil - to remove makeup • Himalaya scrub - to scrub my  face ( twice a week only ) • Mitvana face wash • Nivea moisturiser - I apply a lot of moisturiser n give my face a slight massage. 
Good night my lovelies ❤️😴❤️
